<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/20604371-chasing-tomorrow"><img alt="Chasing Tomorrow (Tracy Whitney #2)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1404962909l/20604371._SX98_.jpg" />
